<surface xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:mith="http://mith.umd.edu/sc/ns1#"
  ulx="0" uly="0" lrx="5406" lry="7276" xml:id="ox-ms_shelley_e1-0092" partOf="#ox-ms_shelley_e1">
  <graphic url="http://shelleygodwinarchive.org/images/ox/ox-ms_shelley_e1-0092.jp2"/>
  <zone type="main">
    <line>The aerial crimson falls, flushing her cheek&#x2013;</line>
    <line>So from our victim's destined agony</line>
    <line>The shade which is our <mod><del rend="strikethrough">shape</del><add place="superlinear"
          >form</add></mod> invests us round</line>
    <line>Else are we shapeless as our Mother <unclear reason="case">N</unclear>ight</line>
    <line rend="center"><milestone unit="tei:speaker" spanTo="#e1-0092.01"/>Prometheus<anchor
        xml:id="e1-0092.01"/></line>
    <line>I laugh your power &amp; his who sent you here</line>
    <line>To lowest scorn.&#x2014; pour forth the cup of pain</line>
    <line rend="center"><milestone unit="tei:speaker" spanTo="#e1-0092.02"/>1.<hi rend="superscript"
        >st</hi> Fury<anchor xml:id="e1-0092.02"/></line>
    <line>Thou thinkest we will rend <mod><del rend="strikethrough">you</del><add
          place="superlinear">thee</add></mod> bone from bone?</line>
    <!-- See above; a Y is overwritten with the "T" in "Thou." -->
    <line>And nerve from nerve, working like fire within?</line>
    <line rend="center"><milestone unit="tei:speaker" spanTo="#e1-0092.03"/>Prometheus<anchor
        xml:id="e1-0092.03"/></line>
    <line>Pain is my element as hate is thine</line>
    <line>Ye rend me now, I care not&#x2014;</line>
    <line rend="center"><milestone unit="tei:speaker" spanTo="#e1-0092.04"/>2.<hi rend="superscript"
        >d</hi> Fury<anchor xml:id="e1-0092.04"/></line>
    <line rend="indent4"> Dost imagine</line>
    <line>We will but laugh into <del rend="strikethrough" instant="true">your</del> thy lidless
      eyes?</line>
    <line rend="center"><milestone unit="tei:speaker" spanTo="#e1-0092.05"/>Prometheus<anchor
        xml:id="e1-0092.05"/></line>
    <line>I weigh not what ye do, but what ye suffer</line>
    <line>Being evil&#x2014;cruel was the Power which called</line>
    <line>You, or aught else so wretched, into light</line>
    <line rend="indent5">
      <metamark function="count">4{6}8</metamark>
    </line>
    <!-- add "line count" to schema? -->
  </zone>
